	<div class="entry" id="entry-7">
					
		<span class="date">June 30, 2005</span>
			<h2><a href="http://blogs.adobe.com/podcast/2005/06/how_to_subscrib.html">How to subscribe to the Macromedia Podcast in iTunes</a></h2>
			<div class="entry-body">
				<p>Here are directions on how to subscribe to the <a href="/podcast/">Macromedia Developer Relations podcast</a> in Apple&#8217;s <a href="http://www.apple.com/itunes/">iTunes</a>.</p>
<ol>
<li>Open <a href="http://www.apple.com/itunes/">iTunes</a></li>
<li>Select Menu &gt; Advanced &gt; Subscribe to Podcast</li>
<li>Enter : http://weblogs.macromedia.com/podcast/index.xml</li>
</ol>
<p>You are now subscribed to the podcast.</p>
			</div>



						
			<div class="meta">
				<span>10:44 AM</span>
